# Inflow Backend

## Prerequisites

You must have the following installed:

- [Golang 1.19](https://go.dev/)

## Environment variables

- deployment/config/dev/.env
- deployment/config/prod/.env

## Local Development
Run service
```bash
    task app:dev --summary
```
## Deployment
There are 2 ways to deploy
1/ Manually run this command: make update-service env=dev service=backend
1/ Use GIT commit message pattern: For ex, to deploy the backend service in your commit message must contain "deploy:backend"

[![Deploy Service](https://github.com/engineeringinflow/inflow-backend/actions/workflows/dev.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/engineeringinflow/inflow-backend/actions/workflows/dev.yml)